    <item>
      <title>Formatação de Números</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/disciplinas/apc-1/formatacao-de-numeros/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/disciplinas/apc-1/formatacao-de-numeros/</guid>
      <description>
        
        
        &lt;p&gt;Em Python, é possível controlar como números são exibidos utilizando formatação. Isso é útil para limitar casas decimais, alinhar valores e melhorar a leitura dos dados.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Formatação com f-string&lt;span class=&#34;hx:absolute hx:-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;formatação-com-f-string&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#formata%c3%a7%c3%a3o-com-f-string&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Link permanente para esta seção&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;A forma mais comum e moderna de formatar números é utilizando &lt;strong&gt;f-strings&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-block hx:relative hx:mt-6 hx:first:mt-0 hx:group/code&#34;&gt;

&lt;div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;background-color:#f7f7f7;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-python&#34; data-lang=&#34;python&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;valor &lt;span style=&#34;color:#0550ae&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#0550ae&#34;&gt;3.14159&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#6639ba&#34;&gt;print&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#1f2328&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#0a3069&#34;&gt;f&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#0a3069&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#0a3069&#34;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;valor&lt;span style=&#34;color:#0a3069&#34;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#0a3069&#34;&gt;.2f&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#0a3069&#34;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#0a3069&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#1f2328&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn-container hx:opacity-0 hx:transition hx:group-hover/code:opacity-100 hx:flex hx:gap-1 hx:absolute hx:m-[11px] hx:right-0 hx:top-0&#34;&gt;
  &lt;button
    class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn hx:group/copybtn hx:cursor-pointer hx:transition-all hx:active:opacity-50 hx:bg-primary-700/5 hx:border hx:border-black/5 hx:text-gray-600 hx:hover:text-gray-900 hx:rounded-md hx:p-1.5 hx:dark:bg-primary-300/10 hx:dark:border-white/10 hx:dark:text-gray-400 hx:dark:hover:text-gray-50&#34;
    title=&#34;Copiar código&#34;
    aria-label=&#34;Copiar código&#34;
    data-copied-label=&#34;Copiado!&#34;
  &gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;hextra-copy-icon hx:group-[.copied]/copybtn:hidden hx:pointer-events-none hx:h-4 hx:w-4&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-success-icon hx:hidden hx:group-[.copied]/copybtn:block hx:pointer-events-none hx:h-4 hx:w-4&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/button&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Neste caso:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;.2f&lt;/code&gt; indica que o número será exibido com &lt;strong&gt;2 casas decimais&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Saída:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-block hx:relative hx:mt-6 hx:first:mt-0 hx:group/code&#34;&gt;

&lt;div&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;3.14&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn-container hx:opacity-0 hx:transition hx:group-hover/code:opacity-100 hx:flex hx:gap-1 hx:absolute hx:m-[11px] hx:right-0 hx:top-0&#34;&gt;
  &lt;button
    class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn hx:group/copybtn hx:cursor-pointer hx:transition-all hx:active:opacity-50 hx:bg-primary-700/5 hx:border hx:border-black/5 hx:text-gray-600 hx:hover:text-gray-900 hx:rounded-md hx:p-1.5 hx:dark:bg-primary-300/10 hx:dark:border-white/10 hx:dark:text-gray-400 hx:dark:hover:text-gray-50&#34;
    title=&#34;Copiar código&#34;
    aria-label=&#34;Copiar código&#34;
    data-copied-label=&#34;Copiado!&#34;
  &gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;hextra-copy-icon hx:group-[.copied]/copybtn:hidden hx:pointer-events-none hx:h-4 hx:w-4&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-success-icon hx:hidden hx:group-[.copied]/copybtn:block hx:pointer-events-none hx:h-4 hx:w-4&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/button&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Casas decimais&lt;span class=&#34;hx:absolute hx:-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;casas-decimais&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#casas-decimais&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Link permanente para esta seção&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-block hx:relative hx:mt-6 hx:first:mt-0 hx:group/code&#34;&gt;

&lt;div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;background-color:#f7f7f7;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-python&#34; data-lang=&#34;python&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;valor &lt;span style=&#34;color:#0550ae&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#0550ae&#34;&gt;10&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#6639ba&#34;&gt;print&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#1f2328&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#0a3069&#34;&gt;f&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#0a3069&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#0a3069&#34;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;valor&lt;span style=&#34;color:#0a3069&#34;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#0a3069&#34;&gt;.2f&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#0a3069&#34;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#0a3069&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#1f2328&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn-container hx:opacity-0 hx:transition hx:group-hover/code:opacity-100 hx:flex hx:gap-1 hx:absolute hx:m-[11px] hx:right-0 hx:top-0&#34;&gt;
  &lt;button
    class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn hx:group/copybtn hx:cursor-pointer hx:transition-all hx:active:opacity-50 hx:bg-primary-700/5 hx:border hx:border-black/5 hx:text-gray-600 hx:hover:text-gray-900 hx:rounded-md hx:p-1.5 hx:dark:bg-primary-300/10 hx:dark:border-white/10 hx:dark:text-gray-400 hx:dark:hover:text-gray-50&#34;
    title=&#34;Copiar código&#34;
    aria-label=&#34;Copiar código&#34;
